      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels through a factory M-variable differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. Recent mechanical attention includes a comprehensive VANOS service and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural and valvetrain integrity. The exterior retains its athletic stance with staggered Style 67 wheels, while the interior features Nappa leather bolsters that remain supportive during spirited cornering. This is a mechanically sound specimen optimized for the purist who values visceral feedback and linear power delivery.",
